      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4-b" mid="147" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'd like to hear about Acrobats.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="93"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Before I craft a new weapon for you, I need to know what path you plan to take. Two options, <FONT color=#a82424>Bow Master</FONT> or <FONT color=#a82424>Acrobat</FONT>. Which Specialization are you curious about?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4" mid="149" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Can you tell me about something else?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4-c" mid="150" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I wish to become a Bow Master.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Bow Master</FONT> is a master of long-range combat, keen of eye and sharp of mind. They tend to favor longbows and crossbows, their skills are designed for these weapons. What do you think?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Once the Specialization is chosen, it will be permanent.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4" mid="152" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Can you tell me about something else?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-4-d" mid="153" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I wish to become an Acrobat.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="151"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Acrobat</FONT> is a close-combat specialist that makes great use of speed and agility. They focus on shortbows to make daring attacks at close, mid-range. What do you think?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Once the Specialization is chosen, it will be permanent.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
